              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A Low-Background B- Proportional Counter with",
                "A Background of Less Than 1 Count Per Minute. The",
                "Efficiency of the Beta Counter was Obtained For All",
                "Nuclides, Except Fo Ga-68 and Ga-70, by Calibration",
                "Against a 4-Pi Counter. The Efficiency For Ga-68 and",
                "Ga-70 was Taken to be the Same As That Ga-73."
              ]
            }
          ],
